title: Australia's "gun control very different to the United States": Turnbull
text:
Australia's "gun control very different to the United States": Turnbull 4:34pm EST - 02:00 
Australian Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull says his country's gun laws that were put in place after a mass shooting in Tasmania in 1996 are ''very different to the United States.''
